description: The old creepy janitor is nowhere to be found perhaps his days of evilness have finally caught up with him. Brenn Wyson is hired as the new janitor and he finds lots of interesting things in the old creepy janitor’s bedroom. It doesn’t take much to push Brenn to the dark side. It doesn’t take long and Brenn has his eyes on Trent Diesel, the football player. Trent doesn’t want anything to do with it and gives the new creepy janitor a lot of attitude. Brenn decides that he will fuck this muscle stud in bondage whether he likes it or not.
title: The New Creepy Janitor
